00/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"btn-ghost flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-base px-8 py-4\" href=\"/dashboard\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-column w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16\"></path><path d=\"M18 17V9\"></path><path d=\"M13 17V5\"></path><path d=\"M8 17v-3\"></path></svg>Live Dashboard</a></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-20 w-full max-w-3xl\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-[40px] font-display font-bold gradient-text mb-1 tracking-tight\">98.7%</div><div class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium\">Detection Accuracy</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-[40px] font-display font-bold gradient-text mb-1 tracking-tight\">&lt;500ms</div><div class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium\">Avg. Latency</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-[40px] font-display font-bold gradient-text mb-1 tracking-tight\">5M+</div><div class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium\">Articles Analyzed</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-[40px] font-display font-bold gradient-text mb-1 tracking-tight\">3</div><div class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium\">AI Models</div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24\"><div class=\"hologram-card p-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6\"><div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-1\">Live Detection Preview</h2><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm\">Real results from our AI pipeline</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"live-dot\"></span><span class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Live</span></div></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4 glass rounded-xl p-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-300 flex-1\">WHO confirms 40% drop in global disease rates in 2024</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 flex-shrink-0\"><span class=\"text-xs font-mono text-slate-500\">94<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"badge-real\">REAL</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4 glass rounded-xl p-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-300 flex-1\">Scientists say drinking bleach cures cancer — government hiding cure</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 flex-shrink-0\"><span class=\"text-xs font-mono text-slate-500\">99<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"badge-fake\">FAKE</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4 glass rounded-xl p-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-300 flex-1\">Federal Reserve raises interest rates by 0.25% amid inflation concerns</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 flex-shrink-0\"><span class=\"text-xs font-mono text-slate-500\">91<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"badge-real\">REAL</span></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-5 text-center\"><a class=\"btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm px-6 py-2.5\" href=\"/analyze\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg> Try With Your Own Article</a></div></div></section><section class=\"relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24\"><div class=\"text-center mb-14\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"ai-chip mx-auto mb-4 font-mono\">Detection Pipeline</div><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight\">How The AI Works</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400 font-light max-w-xl mx-auto\">A 5-stage neural processing pipeline from raw text to verified verdict</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-4\"><div class=\"glass-card p-5 text-center relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"text-xs font-mono text-cyan-500/60 mb-3\">01</div><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-cyan-400/10 border border-cyan-400/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye w-5 h-5 text-cyan-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.062 12.348a1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 19.876 0 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1-19.876 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><div class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-1\">Ingest</div><div class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Article text or URL submitted</div><div class=\"hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 -right-2 w-4 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/50 to-transparent z-10\"></div></div><div class=\"glass-card p-5 text-center relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"text-xs font-mono text-cyan-500/60 mb-3\">02</div><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-cyan-400/10 border border-cyan-400/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=