-1/2 -right-2 w-4 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/50 to-transparent z-10\"></div></div><div class=\"glass-card p-5 text-center relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"text-xs font-mono text-cyan-500/60 mb-3\">04</div><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-cyan-400/10 border border-cyan-400/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-activity w-5 h-5 text-cyan-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-1\">Score</div><div class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Confidence &amp; risk rating</div><div class=\"hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 -right-2 w-4 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/50 to-transparent z-10\"></div></div><div class=\"glass-card p-5 text-center relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"text-xs font-mono text-cyan-500/60 mb-3\">05</div><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-cyan-400/10 border border-cyan-400/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-git-branch w-5 h-5 text-cyan-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 6a9 9 0 0 0-9 9V3\"></path><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"6\" r=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"18\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><div class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-1\">Verdict</div><div class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">FAKE or REAL with reasoning</div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24\"><div class=\"text-center mb-14\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"ai-chip mx-auto mb-4 font-mono\">Capabilities</div><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight\">Everything to Fight Misinformation</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400 font-light text-lg\">A comprehensive AI pipeline from ingestion to verified verdict</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"glass-card p-6 stat-card group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 rounded-xl border flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-400/10 border-cyan-400/20 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-brain w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 18V5\"></path><path d=\"M15 13a4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3-4 4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3 4\"></path><path d=\"M17.598 6.5A3 3 0 1 0 12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.598 1.5\"></path><path d=\"M17.997 5.125a4 4 0 0 1 2.526 5.77\"></path><path d=\"M18 18a4 4 0 0 0 2-7.464\"></path><path d=\"M19.967 17.483A4 4 0 1 1 12 18a4 4 0 1 1-7.967-.517\"></path><path d=\"M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-2-7.464\"></path><path d=\"M6.003 5.125a4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">BERT Transformer AI</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Fine-tuned transformer model delivering &gt;98% accuracy on misinformation detection tasks.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6 stat-card group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 rounded-xl border flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-purple-400 bg-purple-400/10 border-purple-400/20 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Source Credibility</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Real-time trust scoring for news domains with bias detection and historical analysis.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6 stat-card group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 rounded-xl border flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-green-400 bg-green-400/10 border-green-400/20 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21 21-4.34-4.34\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Claim Verification</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Cross-references 5+ trusted news APIs to verify claims in milliseconds.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6 stat-card group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 rounded-xl border flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-orange-400 bg-orange-400/10 border-orange-400/20 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Instant Analysis</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Sub-second AI inference powered by Groq&#x27;s ultra-fast LPU hardware.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6 stat-card group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 rounded-xl border flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-blue-400 bg-blue-400/10 border-blue-400/20 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">URL Scanning</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Paste any URL — we scrape, extract, and analyze the full article automatically.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6 stat-card group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 rounded-xl border flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-red-400 bg-red-400/10 border-red-400/20 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lock w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"11\" x=\"3\" y=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Enterprise Security</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\">JWT-secured API with rate limiting, audit logs, and SOC 2 compliance.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24\">